skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: constance one
des: Constance One provides peace of mind to family caregivers by checking in on their loved ones and summarizing their health and social updates in a daily report. Use the Constance Tip of the Day for useful, interesting ways to improve senior health & living. Simply enable the skill and ask Alexa for the tip anytime. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
